entry.title: Barred From Office by Maduro, This Venezuelan Politician Thinks She Can Still Beat Him
entry.content: Opposition politician Maria Corina Machado wants to challenge the country’s authoritarian president, Nicolás Maduro, at the ballot box. The effort may be hopeless.

entry.title: U.S. Push for Gaza Border Opening Stumbles as Humanitarian Plight Worsens
entry.content: The U.S. is working to get Americans out of the Palestinian enclave and humanitarian aid into it as Israel’s ground offensive looms.
